<plot>A documentary giving film fans a behind-the-scenes look at the making this 2001 film about the arrival of the first refugees from Vietnam after the end of the war. Includes interviews with the cast and crew, who relate some of their experiences with making the film, as well as giving their views on all the work that went into it.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?573906</url></doc>
